	[Pause 8][PrintGrowing]Hmmmmm....[/fx][BR]
	[Pause 10][PrintRising]Let's call it dope![/fx][BR]
	[Pause 15][Wave]Bahaha! No, not drugs![/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	You've been looking better.[BR]
	[Pause 3]Perhaps you [Shake]ARE[/fx] hope after all![Wait][End]
}

