#message:04:086
{
	[Style Right]
	Hello there, friend.[BR]
	[Pause 5]We Bub-Ulbs are the messengers[BR]
	of nature.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Mankind has been soiling the[BR]
	beauty of nature for far too[BR]
	long now.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I look over with peering eyes[BR]
	whenever I see another ounce[BR]
	of technology tear down my late[BR]
	friends and family.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Now don't get me wrong, I am[BR]
	not anti-tech by any means.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I love seeing mankind progress...[BR]
	But...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	That doesn't always give them[BR]
	the right to completely cast[BR]
	aside nature.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Allow me to usher my hopes[BR]
	onto you, good man.[Wait][End]
}

#message:04:087
{
	[Style Right]
