	to restore some nature that[BR]
	has been lost to mankind's lust[BR]
	for technology.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	If you plant it, it'll breathe[BR]
	new life into our soil.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I insist, please consider it.[Wait][End]
}

#message:04:088
